  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/279b99b3d83cd052f149563ddc357e6e.avif?t=1590240957\" width=305 height=92 /></span><br><br>Help Molly achieve her dream of entering the legendary Feria d'Arles - France's greatest bullfighting competition. Meet, betray, and generally become a nuisance to a host of characters. Point and click your way around the French city of Arles, famous for:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>bull fighting<br></li><li>being difficult to pronounce<br></li><li>being where Van Gogh cut his ear off (and painted some masterpieces, I guess.)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/766c4065d6d6941561acae14b8d85e56.poster.avif?t=1590240957\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/766c4065d6d6941561acae14b8d85e56.webm?t=1590240957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/766c4065d6d6941561acae14b8d85e56.mp4?t=1590240957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With glorious pixel-art animation and quirky puzzles, this is a small game about a girl with big dreams.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/03057fe2a759bd60cd5b637a0b0affc7.apng?t=1590240957\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/03057fe2a759bd60cd5b637a0b0affc7.poster.avif?t=1590240957\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=360 /></picture></span><br><br>DISCLAIMER: No bulls were harmed in the making of this game. (One parrot tried to start a fight.)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/ba51a7a0e1a3002b9d5e3527c73c084d.avif?t=1590240957\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pixel-art and animation by Matt Frith.<br></li><li>Illustrations by Jen Pattison.<br></li><li>Original music by Chris Köbke.<br></li><li>Additional writing and design by Alasdair Beckett-King.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181570/extras/607e41953bb99f77668260bbfbf1913e.avif?t=1590240957\" width=640 height=287 /></span><br><br><strong>Controls</strong><br>F1 - Options<br>F5 - Save<br>F7 - Load",
